â”‚  â”‚  - Sequential: Fixed pipeline                        â”‚  â”‚
â”‚  â”‚  - Hierarchical: Supervisor-based                    â”‚  â”‚
â”‚  â”‚  - Decentralized: Peer-to-peer                       â”‚  â”‚
